title: Falco Auto Image
description: Supports a capturing of images from Disk, WEB-Camera, Scanner and correcting for colors. Falco Auto Image gives you comprehensive image editing capabilities to create unique images. This standalone tool with its features and abilities proves to be a boon for professional designers and graphic producers. The advanced auto features of the utility allows in the creation of unique images. The tool has the capability to load images from BMP, GIF, PNG, JPG files, and can save the output images in JPG, GIF, PNG, BMP, formats
